Name: CyberLink PowerDirector 20 Ultra
About the game: Create Professional Level Edits Effortlessly Intuitive editing tools that help you set objects in motion, completely transform a scene's location, and create cinematic effects. Mask & Blend Layer, shape, and blend to create artistic scenes. Green Screen Remove backgrounds and create Hollywood-style special effects. Motion Tracking Add text and graphics that follow the motion of objects to elevate your footage. Limitless Possibilities, Right at Your Fingertips Bring your imagination to life with our wide array of tools to help customize your projects. Customizable Titles Easily create titles with unique customization tools and animated templates. Transitions Choose from a variety of styles to seamlessly connect your shots. Video Effects Transform and modify the look of your video with magical effects. LUTs & Color Match Match color to quickly balance or change the aesthetic of your videos. Screen Recording Capture, edit, and share video demos and tutorials to become the next YouTube star.
